## Source Code (Private Repository)

The ScamBuster source code is **proprietary and not included in this repository**.

Access to the source code is available under the following terms:

### Research & Academic Use

- Available under a **Research License Agreement**
- Requires affiliation with accredited institution
- Non-commercial use only
- Citation required in publications

### Commercial Use

- Available under a **Commercial License Agreement**
- Contact for pricing and terms
- Includes support and updates
- Custom deployment assistance available

### Pilot & Evaluation

- Time-limited evaluation license
- Requires signed agreement
- Scope and success criteria defined upfront
- May lead to commercial license

