## Dataset (Planned Release: February 2026)

The anonymized conversation dataset will be released under **CC BY-NC-SA 4.0** with the following additional terms:

- **Anonymization**: All personally identifiable information removed or hashed
- **Attribution**: Citation of the associated academic publication required
- **Research Use**: Primary intended use is academic research
- **No Re-identification**: Attempts to re-identify individuals are prohibited

